              <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>KEY INSIGHTS</run>
              <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='9'>📈 </run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='9'>Bullish sentiment dominated January and February 2026</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='9'>, reflecting stable market conditions before the geopolitical disruption.</run>
              <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='9'>⚠️ </run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='9'>March 2026 was the only month classified as &quot;Risk-Off,&quot;</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='9'> coinciding with the Strait of Hormuz crisis, a sharp rise in India VIX, and a decline in the Sensex.</run>
              <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='9'>📊 </run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='9'>Market sentiment shifted back to Neutral from April onward</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='9'>, indicating that investor confidence gradually recovered as market volatility eased.</run>
